# Investor Relations

## Company Profile

NewGenIVF Group Limited is an assisted reproductive services (“ARS”) provider in Asia Pacific helping couples and individuals obtain access to fertility treatments. With a mission to assist couples and individuals in building families regardless of fertility challenges, NewGenIVF Group Limited has dedicated itself to creating increased access to fertility treatments and providing mainly two services: (i) in-vitro fertilization (“IVF”) treatment service, comprising traditional IVF and egg donation; and (ii) surrogacy and ancillary caring services. NewGenIVF Group Limited and its management have considerable experience in the ARS market and the broader healthcare industry. NewGenIVF Group Limited’s clinics are located in Thailand, Cambodia, and Kyrgyzstan.
